{"tid":1329228,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警告你地以後, 咪撚用狗這個字來形容班黑警","createTime":"2019-07-18T06:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:55:14.000Z","uid":76310,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"758fdf8992b21657b65731d60fdc229727536f60","tid":1329228,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"警告你地以後, 咪撚用狗這個字來形容班黑警<br />\n<br />\n狗係善良, 忠心的動物<br />\n而黑警只係人形生物的渣滓<br />\n你地用乜字形容都好, 唔可以用狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大把例子證明狗, 用來比喻黑警係毋辱<br />\n<br />\n牠被主人留在路邊，以為主人不久後就會帶自己回家，即使下雨也不敢離開，但是狠心的主人已經將牠拋棄了<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-08-13/CLIPPING/900/20150813003361.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-08-13%2FCLIPPING%2F900%2F20150813003361.jpg&h=34e63db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一隻眼鏡蛇闖入家中，這隻鬥牛犬為了保護主人與蛇搏鬥，雖然牠最後咬死了眼鏡蛇，但自己也中毒身亡，可是死去之前牠還在對著主人搖尾巴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-08-13/900/20150813003378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-08-13%2F900%2F20150813003378.jpg&h=5cc7d284&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淩晨時分家中發生大火，一隻狗狗掙脫項圈喚醒主人。主人雖然逃生，狗狗卻被大火吞沒。主人多次想要衝進火海將狗狗救出，卻因為火勢太大被阻止，現在狗狗的屍體被葬在了他家的院子中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2015-08-13/CLIPPING/900/20150813003387.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2015-08-13%2FCLIPPING%2F900%2F20150813003387.jpg&h=3a4befa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2bdae3fdd4764d960e01208a027986bff4728f6","tid":1329228,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"以後用狗呢個字, 我見一個屌一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班黑警係邪惡政治打壓工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c88af4cb2b60ecb2cb82b235d7021